265
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:11,460
This doesn't amount to any sort of training!

266
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:16,470
Do you know why a person like me would condescend to working up a sweat?

267
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:20,470
It's so I can defeat that pest, Inokuma Yawara.

268
00:17:20,470 --> 00:17:22,470
Now, who's next?



269
00:17:22,470 --> 00:17:23,850
Yes, ma'am!

270
00:17:23,850 --> 00:17:25,230
She's desperate.

271
00:17:25,230 --> 00:17:29,860
Yawara-san means even more to her now.

272
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:31,270
Another reason is that

273
00:17:31,270 --> 00:17:36,780
Yawara-san's father, Mr. Inokuma Kojiro, is still leaning toward being her coach.

274
00:17:36,780 --> 00:17:39,200
B-Big news!

275
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,990
What is it, Tokunaga-san?

276
00:17:40,990 --> 00:17:42,120
H-Here, read this.

277
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:46,750


278
