300
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:02,780
Here! Here!

301
00:19:17,210 --> 00:19:19,340
Nobody's coming.

302
00:19:19,340 --> 00:19:23,300
Don't worry! We were all really into it yesterday, right?

303
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:27,060
I guess it's because I lost yesterday.

304
00:19:27,850 --> 00:19:29,850
