No, you're wrong!

308
00:19:37,780 --> 00:19:39,820
Judo is a very glamorous sport!

309
00:19:40,490 --> 00:19:43,820
Didn't you see how disappointed we were after we lost that match?

310
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:51,750
Why don't we three start practicing?

311
00:20:00,630 --> 00:20:01,970
Paddy-field!




312
00:20:01,970 --> 00:20:05,760
When I said I wanted to see him, he said, "Sure."

313
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:07,930
But then that Katsuo...

314
00:20:07,930 --> 00:20:12,480
He shot me down! That makes him the fourteenth!

315
00:20:12,480 --> 00:20:16,940
I was so pissed I threw him straight to the ground!

316
00:20:21,030 --> 00:20:22,450
Was that what happened?

317
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:26,120
We'll make you stronger, so you can throw more people around!

318
00:20:32,870 --> 00:20:34,120
Yoshinagawa-san!

319
00:20:34,120 --> 00:20:36,000
Look at me!

320
00:20:36,000 --> 00:20:40,050
I lost three kilos at the match!

321
00:20:40,050 --> 00:20:42,760
I must look positively emaciated!

322
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:44,630
You went through a lot yesterday!

323
00:20:45,090 --> 00:20:48,680
I would've lost five kilos if I hadn't eaten afterwards.

324
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:53,140
All right, I'm gonna keep practicing judo and lose more weight!

325
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:53,640
Hi!



326
00:20:54,190 --> 00:20:56,690
Everyone's here!

327
00:20:56,690 --> 00:21:00,690
Oh, my God! Have you seen the papers?

328
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:05,700
