330
00:21:09,950 --> 00:21:13,200
It was like they were ogling a star!

331
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:17,170
It had me wondering, but it turns out I'm a celebrity.

332
00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:21,800
Take a look.

333
00:21:23,800 --> 00:21:28,390
What can I say? A fine showing like mine <i>would</i> make the papers!

334
00:21:28,390 --> 00:21:31,770
Now there's no way I'm quitting judo.

335
00:21:31,770 --> 00:21:33,810
What do you mean, "a fine showing"?

336
00:21:33,810 --> 00:21:35,940
My fine showing. Mine.

337
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:39,440
You saw my picture in the paper, didn't you?

338
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:41,020
What are you, some kind of ghost?

339
