342
00:21:46,990 --> 00:21:48,240
Inokuma-san.

343
00:21:51,330 --> 00:21:52,080
Fujiko-san.

344
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:55,080
See, everybody came.

345
00:21:56,580 --> 00:22:00,500
Judo is a really great sport.



346
00:22:01,250 --> 00:22:02,340
Mm-hmm.

347
00:22:02,340 --> 00:22:04,050
Hey!

348
00:22:04,050 --> 00:22:09,550
It's way past practice time. Why are you standing around gabbing?!

349
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:12,260
When it comes to a great judoka like me,

350
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:16,310
there are no shortcuts to excellence, only practice, practice, practice!

351
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:18,730
Ah, man...

352
00:22:18,730 --> 00:22:20,400
Fine. Let's get on with it.

353
00:22:20,400 --> 00:22:23,270
Wow, I'm a celebrity.

354
00:22:24,230 --> 00:22:29,530
All right, Yawara, Beanpole, quit lazing about and get started!

355
00:22:30,030 --> 00:22:30,450
Yes.

356
00:22:30,450 --> 00:22:31,280
Yes, sir!
Yes.

357
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:35,540
